\end{center}
\end{figure*}

The top left panel of Fig.~\ref{fig:test_RVdifSpec1} shows the 1 signal AK model residuals (i.e., $m = 1$ in Equation~(\ref{eq:orbit1})). The top right panel shows the corresponding GLS periodogram. The remaining panels show the differential periodogram of the residuals for selected period intervals. The $P = 16$ day signal and its one year and daily aliases have been successfully removed. The feature at $P = 6.3$ d is now the highest peak in the residuals.
